{"tid":2071880,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新聞] 全球爆反種族歧視浪潮 嬌生宣布停售美白","createTime":"2020-06-20T07:31:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T13:24:50.000Z","uid":128369,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"4f61bf0af26d5913904cf1217fc193612da18a43","tid":2071880,"uid":128369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T07:31:50.000Z","msg":"時<br />\n<br />\n吳慧珍<br />\n<br />\n全球爆反種族歧視浪潮 嬌生宣布停售美白產品<br />\n<br />\n全球掀起反種族歧視浪潮，標榜可使皮膚白皙透亮的美白產品再度成為箭靶，在強大社會<br />\n壓力下，美國醫療保健大廠嬌生（Johnson &amp; Johnson）19日宣布，決定停售在亞洲和中<br />\n東市場深受歡迎的美白乳液產品。<br />\n<br />\n發言人指出，嬌生打算停賣在印度熱銷的可伶可俐（Clean &amp; Clear）美白系列產品。據<br />\n本月初報導，嬌生將放棄在亞洲與中東地區銷售的露得清細白系列產品（Neutrogena<br />\nFine Fairness）。<br />\n<br />\n嬌生指出，「過去幾周的對話凸顯出，部分產品名稱或淡斑產品聲明所呈現的，是白皙皮<br />\n膚更勝你個人獨特的膚色。那從來不是我們的意圖，健康肌膚就是美麗肌膚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20200620001269-260410?chdtv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20200620001269-260410%3Fchdtv&d=WBYYCruE%2BO8aOQq6cZO2w3HDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=fc6e2231\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20200620001269-260410?chdtv</a>"},{"pid":"4d892137b31098b0f20b72d797a000051733949f","tid":2071880,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T07:34:34.000Z","msg":"爽身粉唔係黑色  係咪歧視？"},{"pid":"9912d6c2a9ba5d7adca5d08c11211a81178086d5","tid":2071880,"uid":46148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T07:37:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />左膠當道"},{"pid":"dea798a33b0c7b78087edd7d8442bdef4a092793","tid":2071880,"uid":35696,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T07:37:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5axP1GQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5axP1GQ.j